data.description: Nestled within the tranquility of a gated mountain community, this expansive home offers a canvas of untapped potential awaiting transformation. Boasting four bedrooms, including a main floor master and two additional bedrooms upstairs, along with an extra bedroom in the basement, this residence provides an ideal layout for both family and guests. With three and a half bathrooms, including an ensuite for the master, and a spacious two-car garage, the home is well-equipped for comfort. The basement holds promise for entertainment with a theater room and additional space that could be converted into an in-law suite. Though in need of upgrades, the mountain home stands as a testament to the possibilities that await, inviting its new owners to envision and unlock the full splendor of mountain living within this exclusive, secure community.
